text: Lou Louise Counil (born 7 November 1985) is a French water polo player. She was a member of the France women's national water polo team at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Yuki Niizawa of Japan shoots, but has her shot saved by Lou Louise Counil Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:French water polo players
